sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as odh-model-controller<br/>Webhook 9443/TCP TLS
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Controllers
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NVCR as nvcr.io Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant ServingAPI as model-serving-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS FIPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over User, ModelReg: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission Webhook (mutate/validate)<br/>TLS, API server cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed (name ≤53 chars)
    K8sAPI-->>User: ISVC Created
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: ISVC created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Route, Service,<br/>ServiceMonitor, KEDA TriggerAuth<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>(auth-delegator for ISVC SA)
    Note right of Controller: DeltaProcessor: compute desired → diff → create/update/delete

    Note over User, ModelReg: Flow 2: NIM Account Provisioning

    User->>K8sAPI: POST Account CR (nim.opendatahub.io)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate: singleton per namespace
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Allowed
    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: Account created
    Controller->>NGC: Validate API Key<br/>Auth: NGC API Key (Bearer)
    NGC-->>Controller: Validation result + model data
    Controller->>NVCR: Get pull token<br/>Auth: NGC API Key (Basic)
    NVCR-->>Controller: Docker auth token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create pull Secret, ConfigMap,<br/>ServingRuntime Template<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

    Note over User, ModelReg: Flow 3: Gateway Discovery (Dashboard)

    Dashboard->>ServingAPI: GET /api/v1/gateways<br/>Auth: User Bearer Token<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ (FIPS ciphers)
    ServingAPI->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>(check user can create llminferenceservices)<br/>Auth: User Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>ServingAPI: Allowed/Denied per namespace
    ServingAPI->>K8sAPI: List Gateways<br/>(filtered by label + RBAC)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>ServingAPI: Gateway list
    ServingAPI-->>Dashboard: JSON: filtered gateways

    Note over User, ModelReg: Flow 4: LLM Auth Policy Management

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: LLMInferenceService created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthPolicy for HTTPRoute<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create EnvoyFilter for Gateway<br/>(Authorino TLS bootstrap)
    Note right of Controller: Gateway-level + per-route auth<br/>managed by separate controllers

    Note over User, ModelReg: Flow 5: Model Registry Sync (Optional)

    Controller->>ModelReg: Sync ISVC metadata<br/>(labels, model IDs)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    ModelReg-->>Controller: Sync result
